<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <div id="_j_photo_264859958" data-seq="264859967" data-pid="264859958" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/264859958.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7auAON2yAA3_VQAA0Qw02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7auAON2yAA3_VQAA0Qw02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264859958" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264861402">
            麻豆：sherry,北大博士在读，胶片爱好者
        </p>
            <div data-seq="264861277" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">故事 + 人像 = ？</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265046844">
            对于一个对<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>历史有点痴迷的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>人来说，能亲身站在「历史现场」完成一组人像作品是一件非常「有意思」但同时又很「有挑战」的事情。<br />
<br />
说「有意思」是因为这些照片都是在有故事、相对小众、一直想去的地点拍摄的。<br />
<br />
说「有挑战」是因为这些地方都是第一次去。对于拍摄环境是什么样完全不了解！<br />
<br />
当「故事」遇见「人像」会发生什么呢&nbsp;？<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="265046977" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">拍摄策划方案</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265047037">
            本次拍摄的摄影器材：<br />
相机：<br />
-&nbsp;单反相机：5D&nbsp;Mark&nbsp;IV<br />
-&nbsp;手机：iPhone&nbsp;7&nbsp;Plus<br />
镜头：<br />
-&nbsp;24-70mm&nbsp;f2.8&nbsp;III<br />
-&nbsp;70-200mm&nbsp;f2.8&nbsp;II&nbsp;<br />
-&nbsp;85mm&nbsp;f1.2&nbsp;II（主力）<br />
<br />
本次拍摄涉及的5个地点。<br />
-&nbsp;鲁迅故居<br />
-&nbsp;福绥境大楼<br />
-&nbsp;白塔寺<br />
-&nbsp;金融街少年宫<br />
-&nbsp;中央音乐学院<br />
tips:这5个地方集中分布在阜成门与复兴门之间。其中前三个互相距离很近，可以算是第一个集中拍摄区域。去另外两个坐公交车4站到达，它们之间距离很近，可以算是第二个集中拍摄区域。<br />
<br />
下面说一下选择这几个拍摄地点的原因。<br />
<br />
最早计划是去白塔寺然后周围有历代帝王庙和广济寺（额。。我对古建筑有点过度痴迷了）但是这样好像很单一，而且在广济寺这样的佛门清净之地拍照也不太合适。所以就做了调整。<br />
<br />
偶然间在网上发现了福绥境大楼这个地方。据说超级神秘，这一下子就把我的好奇心勾起来了。立即将其作为本次拍摄中一个探寻地点。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265047293" data-seq="265047298" data-pid="265047293" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265047293.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/19/EE/wKgBZ1oIbPSAF44fACVKHk-kK4477.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/19/EE/wKgBZ1oIbPSAF44fACVKHk-kK4477.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265047293" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265047698">
            白塔寺就在其附近，我想拍一个胡同中将其作为远景的镜头，所以也将其列入拍摄计划。而鲁迅故居则是在地图上偶然间发现的（结果效果是最好的）也算是顺道去一趟。至此，在阜成门附近的这三个地方算是一个区域，可以集中进行拍摄。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265047777" data-seq="265047779" data-pid="265047777" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265047777.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/3F/wKgBZ1oIbYWADNJBAAxpnkSTTck904.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/3F/wKgBZ1oIbYWADNJBAAxpnkSTTck904.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265047777" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265047987">
            金融街少年宫和中央音乐学院都是以前醇亲王府的一部分。光绪皇帝就是出生在此。所以这是一座潜龙🐲邸（<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>有三座：雍和宫--雍正、醇亲王府（南府）--光绪、醇亲王府（北府）--溥仪）对于这里我是完全未知的！所以超级想去一探究竟。这两个地方离得相当近，可以算是第二个集中的拍摄区域。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265047778" data-seq="265047780" data-pid="265047778" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265047778.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:501px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/40/wKgBZ1oIbYaAPH1RAAelhY3-_-E341.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/40/wKgBZ1oIbYaAPH1RAAelhY3-_-E341.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265047778" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265057034">
            好了，废话不多说，下面介绍一下整个拍摄过程。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="265048609" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">第一站：鲁迅故居</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_265049212" data-seq="265049213" data-pid="265049212" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265049212.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1B/0A/wKgBZ1oIbwGAcoHZABpnOkolLBs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1B/0A/wKgBZ1oIbwGAcoHZABpnOkolLBs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265049212" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265048037">
            鲁迅故居在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>鲁迅博物馆里面，是一个很雅致的小院儿，院子中有当时鲁迅种下的草木。我特别喜欢正房那面的红格子。讨喜的红色加上午后的光影，几乎完美的人像背景~
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264859958" data-seq="265051351" data-pid="264859958" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/264859958.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7auAON2yAA3_VQAA0Qw02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7auAON2yAA3_VQAA0Qw02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264859958" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051339" data-seq="265051357" data-pid="265051339" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
