        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_264859959" data-seq="265051358" data-pid="264859959" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/264859959.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7ayAYdBjAA1jrrAP3f881.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2E/wKgBZ1oH7ayAYdBjAA1jrrAP3f881.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264859959" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051340" data-seq="265051359" data-pid="265051340" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051340.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2C/wKgBZ1oIcR6AWC8XAAm6W8ur5UM76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2C/wKgBZ1oIcR6AWC8XAAm6W8ur5UM76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051340" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265049214">
            当时抓怕了一张sherry用胶片相机📷手动对焦的情景，按下快门后有一声「咔嗒」sherry说那种感觉特别好。好吧，摄影绝对是大坑，玩完数码玩胶片....
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051341" data-seq="265051360" data-pid="265051341" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21847">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051341.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1019px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2C/wKgBZ1oIcR-AW2RDAA1C6h0C-Ac42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2C/wKgBZ1oIcR-AW2RDAA1C6h0C-Ac42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051341" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21847.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21847" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>鲁迅故居
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052152">
            tips:想去鲁迅故居参观的朋友记得带上身份证，凭身份证免费参观。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="265052534" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">第二站：福绥境大楼</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_265047292" data-seq="265051361" data-pid="265047292" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265047292.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/19/EB/wKgBZ1oIbPCAFCSvABvxLFdBvtc87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/19/EB/wKgBZ1oIbPCAFCSvABvxLFdBvtc87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265047292" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052268">
            这个地方离鲁迅故居不远，步行很快就能到达。从外边看和普通居民楼差不多。但是当你走进大楼后，可以在扶手等一些细节上看出这座建筑的年代感。<br />
<br />
走在长长的楼道，有些阴冷，远处昏黄的灯光暗示着这里还有人住。<br />
<br />
刚开始没有找到上楼的电梯，在楼梯拐角处突然跑出一只猫🐱，加上后面骷颅💀的涂鸦，着实吓了我一跳。<br />
<br />
这座大楼电梯有2个，一个好像在维修，据说这里8层（顶层）最神秘，就径直去了8层。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051342" data-seq="265051362" data-pid="265051342" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051342.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2D/wKgBZ1oH7aqAWvTNAAzbZP4Xhj080.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2D/wKgBZ1oH7aqAWvTNAAzbZP4Xhj080.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051342" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052298">
            一出电梯，就是这种颓废感的画面。<br />
<br />
楼道很修长，顶头儿的房子住着人，楼道里电表箱上面的封条时间是2005年7月。才意识到这个楼已经废弃了12年了！当时sherry说如果这时候有个小孩走出来，露出诡异的笑...额，鬼片儿的套路好深啊~
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051343" data-seq="265051363" data-pid="265051343" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051343.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aSAbdNmAA_b7q5C3NY95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aSAbdNmAA_b7q5C3NY95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051343" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052328">
            如果想拍特定类型片子的朋友可以来这里取景。环境氛围绝对到位。<br />
<br />
tips:毕竟是居民区，想来这里看看的朋友还是要轻声细语，另外胆小者慎入，哈哈~<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="265052373" data-index="5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">第三站：白塔寺</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052605">
            从福绥境大楼出来没多远儿，就到了白塔寺。<br />
<br />
白塔寺有一个有趣的地方就是里面的白塔「没有影子」<br />
<br />
当然也不是完全没有影子，只是比较小而已（通过做成「矮胖」的样子来实现😁）据说在元朝的时候白塔寺的面积非常大。有多大呢？当时白塔寺修建的时候是用弓箭🏹拉满射出去，箭落之处才是白塔寺的边界。够大了吧。<br />
<br />
之前进去过白塔寺，但是拍摄效果不太好，可能是「离得太近」的缘故。不过里面的景色还是不错的，有一个<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10069.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="尼泊尔" target="_blank">尼泊尔</a>🇳🇵工匠的塑像在里面，「默默的」讲述着这里的故事。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051344" data-seq="265051364" data-pid="265051344" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3535">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051344.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2F/wKgBZ1oIcSWANmSAABBmMiB_14054.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/2F/wKgBZ1oIcSWANmSAABBmMiB_14054.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051344" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3535.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3535" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>白塔寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052629">
            在外边看白塔还是挺有feel的，可以当做拍照的一个不错的环境背景~
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051345" data-seq="265051365" data-pid="265051345" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3535">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051345.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1019px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aOAGKWRAApw3XsbzqM17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aOAGKWRAApw3XsbzqM17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051345" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3535.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3535" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>白塔寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="265052667" data-index="6" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">第四站：醇亲王府</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265052693">
            最后一站是醇亲王府，也是本次行程最期待的部分~完全未知，充满好奇！！<br />
<br />
知道这个地方，是因为听了一个播客节目，行者掌柜---听<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>（讲的不错，欢迎去收听）从这个节目里得知了醇亲王府是光绪皇帝的出身地。当时就种草了，一定要去看看。<br />
<br />
走进金融街少年宫，终于见到了光绪皇帝的出生地&nbsp;---&nbsp;槐荫斋。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051346" data-seq="265051366" data-pid="265051346" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5849">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051346.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aaAOw9zABhgGFspV-817.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2B/wKgBZ1oH7aaAOw9zABhgGFspV-817.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051346" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5849.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5849" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>醇亲王府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265056187">
            谁会想到这么不起眼儿的小教室，竟会是光绪皇帝的出生地。<br />
<br />
关于槐荫斋，这里还有个传闻。据传光绪的母亲生了好几个孩子，在北屋正房生了一个男孩，但是不幸夭折了。为了避邪，在光绪出生的时候，并没有在北屋而是选择了相对较小的西屋。巧合的是光绪母亲生的几个男孩中，只有光绪长大成人了。<br />
<br />
原先醇亲王府北墙的后罩楼还在，那气势，现在还能感受到！前面的银杏树非常好看，下图便是用拿它当的背景。我很喜欢这张照片，因为它的背景环境太尊贵~
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051347" data-seq="265051367" data-pid="265051347" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5849">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051347.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2D/wKgBZ1oH7aqALsTXABcyyfCYFCg37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2D/wKgBZ1oH7aqALsTXABcyyfCYFCg37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051347" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5849.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5849" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>醇亲王府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265056207">
            原先的老墙有一些还在，厚重肃穆，非常的有感觉。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051348" data-seq="265051368" data-pid="265051348" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5849">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051348.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1019px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/30/wKgBZ1oIcSiAMnesAAlq5AaNyXE10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1C/30/wKgBZ1oIcSiAMnesAAlq5AaNyXE10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051348" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5849.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5849" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>醇亲王府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265056217">
            出了金融街少年宫，步行不到2分钟，就到了中央音乐学院。这两个地方原先都是醇亲王府的一部分，所以距离很近。<br />
<br />
华灯初上的中央音乐学院很美。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051349" data-seq="265051369" data-pid="265051349" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5849">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051349.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2C/wKgBZ1oH7aiAA-WbABmF8WOCFQ428.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2C/wKgBZ1oH7aiAA-WbABmF8WOCFQ428.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051349" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5849.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5849" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>醇亲王府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265056236">
            以此为背景拍照感觉非常好。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265051350" data-seq="265051370" data-pid="265051350" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5849">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265051350.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2C/wKgBZ1oH7aeAK6NbABBqJ8wWlnc18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/2C/wKgBZ1oH7aeAK6NbABBqJ8wWlnc18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265051350" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5849.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5849" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>醇亲王府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="265056290" data-index="7" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">一点儿感触</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265056323">
            时代进步了，但一些有关底蕴的东西似乎正在丢失。复制粘贴式的玻璃幕墙建筑正在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城里拔地而起，似乎只有「新的东西」才能体现城市繁荣。<br />
<br />
但最近特朗普访华，来看的还是故宫，听的还是京剧。故宫是什么？它代表我们的过去和文明，是回答了「我从哪里来」这个严肃哲学问题的地方。展望未来不一定要「抹掉」过去。有时候恰恰是历史教会了我们最多的东西。<br />
<br />
平时没事儿的时候，我总喜欢一个人去这些古建筑、老宅子里面转转。闭上眼，仿佛时空倒转，那是一种说不出的感觉。就像老舍先生曾经描述的一样。<br />
<br />
我所爱的北平，<br />
不是枝枝节节的一些什么<br />
而是整个与我心灵相粘合<br />
一段历史，一大块地方。<br />
我的每一思念中有个北平<br />
这只有说不出而已。<br />
我不能爱<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>与<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10320.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="天津" target="_blank">天津</a>，<br />
因为我心中有个北平。<br />
可是我说不出来！<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;---&nbsp;老舍&nbsp;「想北平」<br />
<br />
更多精彩内容，可以关注的我的微信公众号yandesign<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/6@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265056468" data-seq="265056469" data-pid="265056468" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7923991/265056468.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1F/02/wKgBZ1oIda2AOMHIAAG8EwXNxWc93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1F/02/wKgBZ1oIda2AOMHIAAG8EwXNxWc93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265056468" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
    
